Argumentative:2:1 My little children, these things write I unto you, that ye sin not.
Argumentative:And if any man sin, we have an advocate with the Father, Jesus Christ the righteous: 2:2 And he is the propitiation for our sins: and not for our's only, but also for the sins of the whole world.
Argumentative:2:3 And hereby we do know that we know him, if we keep his commandments.
